Rubicon Technology, Inc.







Rubicon Technology, Inc.Street Address: 900 E Green st unit ABensenvilleILUnited States60106Web Site Address: http://www.rubicontechnology.com
Company Description: Rubicon Technology is a leading materials science solutions provider in the research, manufacturing, marketing and distribution of high-quality single crystal sapphire and other advanced technology materials. Our Chicago based crystal growth, fabrication, polishing and cleaning facilities provide a consistent supply of the highest quality EPI ready substrates, windows, rods, rodstock, lenses, tubes, blanks and boules coupled with excellent service. Rubicon uses the proprietary KYR-Plus crystal growth method and technology to grow the finest quality, large-diameter and high-density single crystal sapphire in all orientations. Rubicon's sapphire products have a lower dislocation density or edge pit density (EPD), higher transmission in the UV range, are ultra flat, EPI-ready clean, uniformly flat and consistent and precise tolerances. These qualities make our polished substrates an ideal choice for white, blue and HB LEDs, LDs, Opto-electronic, telecommunications, optical & laser, compound semiconductor and semiconductor fabrication applications. Rubicon also offers quartz, cesium iodide, germanium, magnesium fluoride, calcium fluoride, lithium fluoride, barium fluoride, zinc oxide and other exotic materials.
Company ID: 9976Join Date: Feb 18, 2015 

Address Map: 
Primary Industry: SemiconductorPrimary Product Category: MaterialsPrimary Product Sub Category: Wafers    




 



 
 







 








 

 





















